videos.description: With a chance to put the game away, Colorado's Jaylyn Sherrod misses two consecutive freethrows and Endyia Rogers races down the court to bring Oregon within striking distance.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Oregon capitalizes on Jaylyn Sherrod missed FTs) 2022/02/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon capitalizes on Jaylyn Sherrod missed FTs

videos.description: Quay Miller makes a contested hook shot to increase Colorado's lead to 84-80 over Oregon with three minutes left in the second overtime period.
